    "title": "Maono",
    "media_type": "Text",
    "index_reference": "maono",
    "language": "swh",
    "content": "<p>Maono ni sawa na uzoefu mwingine wa Ufunuo wa Mungu, kama vile ndoto (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:5-Gen37:10\">Mwanzo 37:5–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:5-Gen40:19\">40:5–19</a>). Mifano maarufu ni pamoja na maono ya nabii Ezekieli kuhusu bonde la mifupa mikavu na maono ya nabii Isaya kuhusu kiti cha enzi cha Mungu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:1-Ezek37:14\">Ezekieli 37:1–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:1-Isa6:13\">Isaya 6</a>). Manabii wa Agano la Kale mara nyingi walipokea ujumbe kutoka kwa Bwana kupitia maono. Maono katika Biblia mara nyingi yalionyesha picha zenye nguvu na za kukumbukwa ambazo zilisaidia watu kuelewa ujumbe wa Mungu. Katika maono haya, Mungu alionyesha picha maalum au mandhari ambazo zilikuwa na maana za kina kuhusu mambo halisi yanayotokea duniani. Mungu au malaika kisha wangemweleza mtu huyo maana ya picha hizi.</p><p>Maono ni muhimu katika kitabu cha Matendo na mara nyingi hutokea wakati wa maombi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:10-Acts9:12\">Matendo 9:10–12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:9\">16:9–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:17-Acts22:21\">22:17–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:11\">23:11</a>; tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:8-Luke1:20\">Luka 1:8–20</a>). Katika tukio moja, malaika alimtembelea Kornelio, afisa wa Kirumi (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:1-Acts10:6\">Matendo 10:1–6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:30-Acts10:32\">30–32</a>). Malaika alimwambia atume kwa mtume Petro. Siku iliyofuata, Petro alipokuwa akiomba, aliona maono (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:9-Acts10:16\">10:9–16</a>; tazama <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:5-Acts11:10\">11:5–10</a>). Maono hayo yalihusiana na mkutano wake na Kornelio.</p><p>Kwenye Matendo 9, maono ya mtume Paulo na Ananiasi yanaonyesha jukumu la Mungu katika maisha yao (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:3-Acts9:6\">9:3–6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:10-Acts9:16\">10–16</a>). Maono haya si ya bahati mbaya bali ni sehemu ya mpango wa Mungu wa kuokoa ulimwengu.</p><p>Maono yanatoa mwongozo wa kiungu na kuwaonyesha wafanyakazi Wakristo jinsi ya kutekeleza Agizo Kuu.</p><p>Paulo alipata maono kadhaa:</p><ul><li><p>wakati wa kuongoka kwake kwenye barabara ya Dameski (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:3-Acts9:6\">Matendo 9:3–6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:6-Acts22:10\">22:6–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:12-Acts26:19\">26:12–19</a>)</p></li><li><p>Kabla ya safari yake ya umishonari kwenda Ulaya (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:9\">16:9</a>)</p></li><li><p>katika Korintho (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:9-Acts18:11\">18:9–11</a>)</p></li><li><p>katika hekalu (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:17-Acts22:21\">22:17–21</a>)</p></li><li><p>katika Yerusalemu kabla ya safari yake kwenda Roma (<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:11\">23:11</a>)</p></li></ul><p>Kupitia maono, Mungu anaongoza kwa ufanisi shughuli za kanisa na kupanua misheni yake (tazama maelezo ya masomo kwenye <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"8467\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">Matendo 10:3</span>, <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"8471\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">9–16</span>; <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"8667\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">22:17–22</span>; <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"8672\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">23:11</span>; tazama pia <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:8-Gal1:9\">Wagalatia 1:8–9</a> na <span data-bnType=\"resourceReference\" data-resourceId=\"11250\" data-resourceType=\"TyndaleStudyNotes\">maelezo ya somo hapo</span>).</p><p><u>Sehemu za Kujifunza Zaidi</u></p><p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen37:5-Gen37:10\">Mwanzo 37:5–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:1-Gen41:36\">40:1–41:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa6:1-Isa6:13\">Isaya 6:1–13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer14:14\">Yeremia 14:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek37:1-Ezek37:14\">Ezekieli 37:1–14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan8:1-Dan8:27\">Danieli 8:1–27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:21\">9:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos12:10\">Hosea 12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Obad1:1\">Obadia 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:3\">Habakuki 2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:8-Luke1:20\">Luka 1:8–20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:3-Acts9:6\">Matendo 9:3–6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts9:10-Acts9:16\">10–16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:3-Acts10:6\">10:3–6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:9-Acts10:16\">9–16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:30-Acts10:32\">30–32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:5-Acts11:9\">11:5–9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:9-Acts16:10\">16:9–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts18:9-Acts18:11\">18:9–11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:6-Acts22:10\">22:6–10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:17-Acts22:21\">17–21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:11\">23:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts26:14-Acts26:19\">26:14–19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:1-2Cor12:10\">2 Wakorintho 12:1–10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev1:9-Rev22:7\">Ufunuo 1:9–22:7</a></p>",
